You can simply switch from video on your tablet to a call on your mobile phone so you never miss an important call. And the light and compact folding design makes these headphones always ready to travel, wherever you go.

description: PRO X gaming headset with support for BLUE VO technology! DTS HEADPHONE: X 2.0 - the latest version of the surround sound system, which takes into account the distance to objects from DTS. In version 2.0, the surround sound of the channel in 7.1 format has been improved thanks to improved bass transmission, sound clarity and zoom targets. And most importantly - thanks to a new method of determining the distance, you can now estimate the distance to the sound source to even more accurately calculate the location of your opponent!

name: Logitech
description: Large diffusers with a diameter of 50 mm provide stunning sound quality, giving the player the opportunity to dive deeper into the game. Favorite games will finally sound the way the developers intended: just great. Thanks to the 6 mm microphone, the player will never lose touch with his teammates. The mute-up mute feature allows you to mute the voice and remove the microphone when you don't need it. Using a cable with a 3.5 mm headphone plug can be connected to a PC or Mac, as well as mobile devices and game consoles, including PlayStation 4, Xbox One and Nintendo Switch. Each element of the headphones is designed in such a way as to provide the user with maximum comfort. Luxurious lightweight faux leather earmuffs and headbands are extremely comfortable and do not press on the ears. For greater convenience, the ear cushions can be rotated at an angle of up to 90 °. One of the headphones has a wheel with which you can easily adjust the volume regardless of the platform used.

name: Logitech
description: Forward to the game! Wherever you are, immerse yourself in the virtual world with your head. G333 gaming headphones sound great and provide quality communication when used with a variety of mobile devices, as well as PCs, game consoles Xbox, PlayStation, Nintendo and others. They can be connected via a 3.5 mm jack or USB-C adapter (supplied). Dual dynamic game class diffusers. G333 gaming headphones have been created to make the gaming process even more exciting. Special dual diffusers (one for high and mid frequencies, the other for low frequencies) transmit rich sound that accurately reproduces events in the virtual world. Built-in microphone and cable controls. High-quality built-in microphone provides clear transmission of voice commands and user cues in the chat, and thanks to integrated controls, you can easily start and stop playback, as well as adjust the volume. Among other things, this microphone allows you to answer calls directly during the game.
